From 95007274ddef8126a7682690602122e0b8390a24 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dr Hannah Sanford-Crane <hannah@maadscientist.com>
Date: Thu, 5 Mar 2026 20:46:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Glycan module: scorer + contact maps + G3-V MIT DFT
 cross-validation
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

New files:
  glycan/contact_maps.py  — Full contact maps for ConA/WGA/PNA/Gal3/Davis
      - 5 scaffolds, 21 ligands, each with n_HB/buried/n_CHP/res_type/
        n_linker/anchor/obs_dG/confidence/note
      - Structural sources: PDB 5CNA, 1CVN, 2UVO, 2PEL, 3GAL, Eades 2026
  glycan/scorer.py        — GlycanScorer class
      - score(scaffold, ligand) -> GlycanPrediction
      - score_scaffold() / score_all()
      - compute_r2() with optional confidence filter
      - DG0 computed at runtime from anchor ligand; Davis pre-anchored
  glycan/g3v_mit_dft.py   — Phase G3-V MIT DFT cross-validation
      - Attempts Zenodo download (DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.15062118)
      - Falls back to paper-reported DFT values (Keys 2025 Fig 3)
      - Applies solvent attenuation f_solv=0.25 (Asensio 2013)
      - 2x pass criterion: all 3 residue types PASS
  glycan/tests/test_glycan_scorer.py — 49 tests

Results (v2.3 locked parameters):
  All entries (n=21):   R²=0.935  MAE=0.83 kJ/mol  RMSE=1.59
  HIGH only  (n=15):   R²=0.985  MAE=0.41 kJ/mol  RMSE=0.54

G3-V cross-validation:
  Trp: MABE=-3.50 | DFT_att=[-6.15,-2.64] | ratio=0.80 PASS
  Tyr: MABE=-1.90 | DFT_att=[-4.10,-1.76] | ratio=0.65 PASS
  Phe: MABE=-1.90 | DFT_att=[-3.37,-1.44] | ratio=0.79 PASS

Key validations:
  - ConA: Man > Glc selectivity correct (PASS)
  - Davis: Glc > Gal > Man correct (PASS)
  - WGA oligomer ordering correct (PASS)
  - OPPOSITE selectivity ConA vs Davis with SAME parameters (PASS)

Total tests: 610 pass, 50 skip, 0 fail (was 561).
